    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and she\u2019s been absolute gold to me. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014runs like a dream and has been super well-loved over the years. You\u2019ll find it\u2019s got plenty of life left for all your adventures! Perfect for someone looking for a reliable car that\u2019s been taken care of. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
