    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This 2017 Porsche Macan S in Volcano Grey Metallic is a standout example of a well-cared-for performance SUV. The exterior paint retains a deep, lustrous shine, with only a few minor stone chips on the front bumper and a small, professionally touched-up scratch on the rear passenger door. The 20-inch RS Spyder Design wheels are in excellent shape, showing minimal curb rash. Inside, the Agate Grey leather interior remains supple and clean; the seats show very light creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster, but there are no tears or unpleasant odors. All cabin technology, including the panoramic sunroof and Bose Surround Sound system, operates flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is robust, backed by a comprehensive service log and a recent 40,000-mile major service. The tires are matching Pirellis with roughly 70% tread depth remaining. This is a reliable, turn-key vehicle that has been driven with respect and maintained without compromise.",
      "price": 35500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
